{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "人与龙的契约之证 第25章 4-1 魔神王",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "王子为了见证泽娜的决心，\\n与她一同前往泽娜的世界。\\n二人在那里遇到了被魔神附身\\n并意图毁灭世界的异界王子，\\n昔日的回忆让泽娜无畏地向魔神发起挑战。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这里就是你的世界啊……\\n没想到圣城已经破败成\\n这个样子了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "这里在狄涅尔帝国的进攻下沦陷。\\n后来因无人治理而变为废墟。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是吗……\\n这也是我所造成的结果啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "你不必归咎于自己。\\n就像我和塞西娅是不同的人一样，\\n这个世界的哥哥与你也是不同的人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不……这件事我也不能置身事外。\\n因为我也曾经差点将身体交给魔神……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "对不起，各位。\\n我知道这是对相信我、\\n追随我之人的背叛……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但是……现在能救塞西娅的\\n就只有我了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "纳姆，抱歉……\\n大家，抱歉……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呃、呜、呜啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皇帝塞西娅",
            "context": "呵呵……呵哈哈哈哈哈哈！\\n马上……就差一点了！\\n令人忌惮的圣域龙的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "你也真可悲呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "魔神啊，\\n你将要成为的是我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "当时是贝维特哥哥\\n出现夺走了魔神之力，\\n我才幸免于难。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但这只是结果论。\\n无论如何，我都曾做出过\\n会导致世界毁灭的决定。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "哥哥……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以如今我才必须要\\n为拯救世界而竭尽全力。\\n没有时间让我沮丧了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "是啊……\\n我也要做我该做的事才行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "总之，虽然不清楚来到异界\\n会受到怎样的影响，\\n但能在到这边后立刻见到你真是太好了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你现在这已经是\\n真正的身体了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "是的。这不是意念体，\\n而是我真正的身体。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "真不可思议……\\n我还以为自己已经习惯了意念体，\\n与真身没有什么区别……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "但现在我能感觉到自己充满了力量。\\n这样的话……\\n说不定真的可以掌握创世之力！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "真是太好了。\\n既然如此，\\n就只剩下“因果之枷锁”的问题了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "斩断“因果之枷锁”需要\\n举行仪式。为此要用魔导书……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07",
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "二人",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "那是泽诺斯的终端！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔，\\n他是打算把这个世界也毁灭掉吗……\\n休想得逞！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "异界裂缝正在扩大……\\n这样下去的话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "异界裂缝就交给我吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "我以起始之人的名义在此号令——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "泽娜！\\n你已经能掌控创世之力了吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "嗯！有这肉体在的话……\\n我似乎也可以做到！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好，那我来对付终端！\\n你趁此尽量关闭裂缝。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "原来如此……\\n我说这些终端怎么会躁动不安……\\n原来是来了稀客。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔……\\n你、你是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "哥哥！不……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是这个世界里……\\n被魔神附身的我吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "好久没见到你，\\n还以为你已经死在哪里了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "原来你是去异界求助了啊，我的妹妹。\\n你明知那都是些无用的挣扎。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "魔神莫尔托梅塞亚！\\n不准你叫我妹妹！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "莫尔托梅塞亚吗……\\n这个名字早已配不上我了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔神王",
            "context": "我乃王。统领人类、驾驭群龙、\\n统治世界之王。亦是引导世界\\n走向终焉的末日之王！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "魔神……你可知道，\\n现在很多世界都处在危机之中。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "因为“起始之人”，\\n所有可能性的世界都将要消失。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "就连你称霸的这个世界也不例外。\\n你明白这点吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔神王",
            "context": "当然。\\n我是诞生自黑暗魔力的仇恨化身。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔神王",
            "context": "黑暗魔力是“起始之人”的愤怒，\\n他要做什么我自然了如指掌。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "也就是说……你和莫尔提斯一样吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔神王",
            "context": "但这个世界是我的世界。\\n我可不会假手于“起始之人”！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔神王",
            "context": "只有我亲手毁灭这个世界，\\n我的复仇才算完美！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "复仇……向圣域龙复仇吗。\\n可是圣域龙已经死了啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔神王",
            "context": "是啊。那家伙在我眼前消失，\\n一定是有哪个家伙在背地里\\n多管闲事了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔神王",
            "context": "明明应该由我来手刃那家伙……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔神王",
            "context": "不过就算圣域龙死了，\\n我的复仇也不会停止。\\n我是永远不会原谅那家伙的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔神王",
            "context": "不把那家伙所深爱的这个世界，\\n所守护的这个世界毁灭殆尽，\\n我的复仇就不算完成！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "好吧……魔神啊，\\n我也一样，\\n无论发生什么事我都无法原谅你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "今天我一定要让你\\n将那身躯——将我哥哥还给我！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_25_08_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}